OL,3,CCar wash bosses led 'double life' in
OL,4,Crunning 'huge' people smuggling ring
OL,6,FTwo men who appeared to be successful
OL,7,Fcar wash owners in Caerphilly have
OL,8,Fbeen convicted after they were
OL,9,Fdiscovered to be running a 'huge'
OL,10,Fpeople smuggling ring.
OL,12,FDilshad Shamo, 41, and Ali Khdir, 40,
OL,13,Fwere working as part of a larger
OL,14,Forganised crime group to move
OL,15,Fthousands of migrants across Europe.
OL,17,FMigrants were offered three tiers of
OL,18,Fservice ` the simplest being on foot
OL,19,For via HGV or smaller vehicle, the
OL,20,Fnext by cargo ships or yachts, and the
OL,21,Ftop tier by providing plane travel.
