OL,3,CCar wash bosses led 'double life' in
OL,4,Crunning 'huge' people smuggling ring
OL,6,FMigrants came from Iraq, Iran and
OL,7,FSyria through Turkey, Belarus, Moldova
OL,8,Fand Bosnia and ending in Italy,
OL,9,FCroatia, Romania, Bulgaria, Slovenia,
OL,10,FGermany and France. Many of them are
OL,11,Fsuspected of arriving in the UK,
OL,12,Faccording to the National Crime Agency.
OL,14,FThe pair also used messaging and
OL,15,Fsocial media apps to advertise their
OL,16,Froutes by sending videos from people
OL,17,Fwho had already taken the journey.
