OL,3,CCar wash bosses led 'double life' in
OL,4,Crunning 'huge' people smuggling ring
OL,6,FDilshad Shamo and Ali Khdir were
OL,7,Fcharged in February 2024 with offences
OL,8,Fof facilitation of migrants through
OL,9,FEurope following a National Crime
OL,10,FAgency investigation, supported by
OL,11,FGwent Police.
OL,13,FAfter a ten-day trial at Cardiff Crown
OL,14,FCourt, both pleaded guilty to all
OL,15,Foffences today (22 November). A
OL,16,Ffurther hearing will be held on Monday
OL,17,Fahead of sentencing.
OL,19,FNCA Branch Commander Derek Evans said
OL,20,FAli Khdir and Dilshad Shamo were
OL,21,Fleading "a double life."
