OL,6,FHe said: "We worked painstakingly to
OL,7,Fpiece together their movements to
OL,8,Fprove their important roles in a
OL,9,Fgroup, from advertising their services
OL,10,Fthrough videos to boasting of
OL,11,Fsuccessful trips on messaging groups.
OL,13,F"Tackling organised immigration crime
OL,14,Fis a top priority for the NCA and we
OL,15,Fwill continue to do all we can to
OL,16,Fbring those involved in people
OL,17,Fsmuggling networks to justice."
