OL,6,FMinister for Border Security and
OL,7,FAsylum, Dame Angela Eagle, said: "We
OL,8,Fare taking action against the people
OL,9,Fsmuggling gangs and will stop at
OL,10,Fnothing to dismantle their networks
OL,11,Fand bring justice to the system.
OL,13,F"Our new Border Security Command will
OL,14,Fintensify our efforts to disrupt the
OL,15,Fcriminal gangs with cutting edge
OL,16,Ftechnology and increased efforts in
OL,17,Ftransit countries to prevent unsafe
OL,18,Fsmall boat equipment reaching the
OL,19,FFrench coast.
